Maxima still in her tiger form, then barely transformed to robot mode, 
stumbled & barely stablized as she looked up at him. Shaking her head, "She was to 
remain inside to assist with the defenses." pausing. "Hopefully. But 
unfortunately, she has a meta processor all of her own." Maxima sounded rather annoyed & 
grave. She herself was coming to her maximum limit for remaining in action 
while wounded & more.
